            <title>[SPARK-3072] Yarn AM not always properly exiting after unregistering from RM</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-3072</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The yarn application master doesn&apos;t always exit properly after unregistering from the RM.  &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;One way to reproduce is to ask for large containers (&amp;gt; 4g) but use jdk32 so that all of them fail.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
